text: Paulilatino (Paùlle) is a town and comune (municipality) in the Province of Oristano in Sardinia, Italy. As of 2016, 2,234 people lived there. Its area is 103.85 km². It is 280 meters above sea level. == References == == Other websites == Category:Communes of the Province of Oristano
title: Paulilatino
